title: No. 7 Michigan State pulls away for 52-26 win over Indiana
text:
> Indiana No. 7 Michigan State pulls away for 52-26 win over Indiana Indiana kicker Griffin Oakes reacts after missing an extra point during the second quarter of an NCAA college football game against Michigan State, Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015, in East Lansing, Mich.
